{"text_id":23085,"tokens":["Participating"," in"," sports"," is"," an"," integral"," part"," of"," many"," students","'"," educational"," experiences",","," as"," it"," helps"," foster"," physical"," fitness",","," teamwork",","," and"," discipline","."," Consequently",","," decisions"," surrounding"," student"," athletic"," participation"," should"," prioritize"," creating"," a"," positive"," and"," inclusive"," environment"," while"," also"," promoting"," healthy"," competition","."," ","\n\n","One"," perspective"," on"," whether"," students"," should"," be"," required"," to"," have"," a"," letter"," B"," grade"," or"," above"," to"," participate"," in"," sports"," is"," that"," it"," encourages"," students"," to"," maintain"," good"," academic"," standing","."," By"," setting"," this"," requirement",","," students"," are"," motivated"," to"," prioritize"," their"," studies"," as"," well"," as"," their"," athletic"," pursuits",","," leading"," to"," a"," balanced"," approach"," to"," school","."," Additionally",","," this"," policy"," may"," help"," schools"," identify"," students"," who"," are"," struggling"," academically"," and"," provide"," them"," with"," the"," support"," they"," need"," to"," succeed"," in"," both"," academics"," and"," sports",".","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," some"," argue"," that"," linking"," academic"," performance"," to"," sports"," participation"," could"," lead"," to"," an"," overly"," competitive"," environment"," that"," prioriti","zes"," grades"," over"," personal"," growth"," and"," sports","manship","."," Consequently",","," this"," could"," potentially"," discourage"," students"," who"," struggle"," in"," traditional"," academic"," settings"," or"," have"," learning"," differences"," from"," pursuing"," sports"," altogether",","," negatively"," impacting"," their"," physical"," and"," mental"," well","-","being","."," ","\n\n","In"," my"," view",","," while"," there"," may"," be"," cases"," where"," students"," excel"," in"," sports"," but"," struggle"," academically",","," establishing"," a"," blanket"," requirement"," of"," a"," letter"," B"," grade"," or"," above"," could"," discourage"," students"," from"," pursuing"," their"," athletic"," passions","."," A"," more"," balanced"," approach"," could"," be"," to"," encourage"," students"," to"," maintain"," a"," reasonable"," GPA"," while"," also"," offering"," additional"," academic"," support"," and"," resources"," to"," students"," who"," engage"," in"," sports","."," ","\n\n","To"," address"," the"," cons"," of"," an"," overly"," competitive"," environment",","," schools"," could"," also"," consider"," promoting"," a"," more"," holistic"," view"," of"," student"," success",","," which"," includes"," fostering"," well","-","rounded"," individuals"," through"," extracurricular"," activities"," like"," sports",","," community"," service",","," and"," student"," government","."," By"," encouraging"," students"," to"," explore"," various"," interests"," and"," passions",","," schools"," can"," create"," a"," more"," inclusive"," and"," diverse"," student"," body",","," thereby"," enhancing"," the"," overall"," educational"," experience"," for"," all"," students","."," ","\n\n","Ultimately",","," the"," decision"," to"," require"," a"," letter"," B"," grade"," or"," above"," for"," sports"," participation"," should"," be"," made"," on"," a"," case","-","by","-","case"," basis",","," taking"," into"," consideration"," the"," unique"," needs"," and"," circumstances"," of"," each"," school"," and"," student"," body","."," By"," prioriti","sing"," the"," education"," and"," well","-","being"," of"," students",","," schools"," can"," create"," an"," environment"," that"," fosters"," both"," academic"," and"," athletic"," success","."," ","\n\n","Would"," you"," like"," me"," to"," expand"," on"," any"," of"," the"," points"," made"," above","?"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"cohere","label":1}